HEADWORD: Alliterate
<hw>Al*lit"er*ate</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To employ
or place so as to make alliteration.</def> <rj><au>Skeat.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

