==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Alliterate
<hw>Al*lit"er*ate</hw>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To compose alliteratively;
also, to constitute alliteration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Alliteration</ent>⟦br⟧
